DISCLAIMER
As of 2026-03-16, the repository (`magtools/warp-engine`) is the historical
fork where maintenance continued after upstream inactivity. Active derived work
now continues at `https://github.com/magtools/phoenix-launch-silo`.

`magtools/warp-engine` is a GitHub fork of:
`https://github.com/ArturoI/warp-engine` (GitHub `parent` metadata).

As of 2026-03-16, `ArturoI/warp-engine` is marked on GitHub as `fork: false`
and its latest upstream push date shown by GitHub is 2019-04-08.

Historical references in this project point to Summa infrastructure/repository
(`ct.summasolutions.net` and `SummaSolutions/warp-engine`), while the public
`SummaSolutions/warp-engine` repository endpoint is currently not available
on GitHub (HTTP 404 as of 2026-03-16).
